description: TrStSaNrFreqRelProfile: This table stores parameters of the NR frequency relation profile for a given cell at a specific time, including identifiers and metadata.  dateTime: Timestamp of the record; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell; Id2: Redundant cell identifier; Id3:  Ancillary identifier (likely internal); Id4: Ancillary identifier (likely indicating a default profile); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format; TrStSaNrFreqRelProfile.trStSaNrFreqRelProfileId: Profile identifier; TrStSaNrFreqRelProfile.userLabel: User-defined label; TrStSaNrFreqRelProfile.reservedBy:  Indicates if the profile is reserved.
